<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27May1929"><font color="red">27 May 1929</font> <i>Selected Letters</i> (to Harriet Weaver): O is out today &hellip; I gave the title &lsquo;Tales Told of Shem and Shaun&rsquo; to the Crosbye&apos;s book. J.N.W. Sullivan having declined to do the preface I proposed to them C.K. Ogden (author in part of The Meaning of Meaning) who did a very useful introduction &hellip; The book is out on Saturday [1 June 1929] &hellip;  </div>
